@page "/"

<PageTitle>Greener Admin</PageTitle>

<h1 class="display-6 mb-3">Welcome to Greener Admin</h1>
<p>
    This hosted Blazor WebAssembly experience demonstrates how the legacy WPF configurator can be modernised.
    Use the navigation menu to manage <strong>locations</strong>, <strong>rules</strong>, and the rest of the platform assets.
</p>

<div class="row gy-4">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h5">Locations</h2>
                <p>Browse, create, and update locations plus their nested floor details.</p>
                <NavLink class="btn btn-primary" href="locations">Open locations</NavLink>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h5">Rules</h2>
                <p>Review operational rules, update the schedule, or deactivate noisy alerts.</p>
                <NavLink class="btn btn-primary" href="rules">Open rules</NavLink>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h5">Documentation</h2>
                <p>Need the bigger picture? The implementation guide explains the full roadmap.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank" href="docs/ImplementationGuide.md">Read the guide</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
